snippet.title: Aeschylus Life Changing Quotes
snippet.description:
Aeschylus Life Changing Quotes. Listen Some Brilliant Quotes From The father of tragedy Aeschylus. Aeschylus was an ancient Greek tragedian, and is often described as the father of tragedy. Academic knowledge of the genre begins with his work, and understanding of earlier Greek tragedy is largely based on inferences made from reading his surviving plays.

These are vivid sayings and quotes from Aeschylus. The best quotes and aphorisms of Aeschylus that will make you think about many things in life. Life quotes from Aeschylus are definitely worth your time.

Thank you for watching!
